snippet.title: Pinball M: Duke Nukem's Big Shot Pinball - Official Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description: Here's your look at the Duke Nukem's Big Shot Pinball table in this latest Pinball M trailer. Duke Nukem's Big Shot Pinball will be available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC (via Epic Games and Steam).
